=head1 DESCRIPTION

Describes the deletion state of an Amazon Route 53 hosted zone for a
domain that is being automatically delegated to an Amazon Lightsail DNS
zone.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Code => Str

The status code for the deletion state.

Following are the possible values:

=over

=item *

C<SUCCEEDED> - The hosted zone was successfully deleted.

=item *

C<PENDING> - The hosted zone deletion is in progress.

=item *

C<FAILED> - The hosted zone deletion failed.

=item *

C<STARTED> - The hosted zone deletion started.

=back



=head2 Message => Str

The message that describes the reason for the status code.



